

	 
         I could easily kill a cactus in under a week, so if I everwant a gardenI'll need to plant everything in  urlLink Wonder Soil . Wonder Soil is fertilizer-rich dehydrated peat which expands when you add water. One 14 oz. container is equivalent to 10 lbs. of regular soil. Polymers in the soil time-release water so if you're a once a week (or month) waterer like I am, your plants may still survive.  
     
    
